{"tid":216733,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有無巴絲打知道酒精嘅計算方法?","createTime":"2017-04-25T11:43:19.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-25T16:21:27.000Z","uid":87396,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"93714b9694d0be58c31860dc6d20b9ae36b33f85","tid":216733,"uid":87396,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-25T11:43:19.000Z","msg":"一罐大啤酒(500ml)當佢酒精濃度係4%<br />\n一支紅酒(750ml)係12%<br />\n姐係飲三罐啤酒等於一支紅酒?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但係點解飲3罐啤酒無感覺<br />\n但係一支紅酒會有上腦嘅感覺?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n想知好耐其實佢個酒精濃度係點樣計算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n飲吖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1164c5c1123936eaedefe5b1d42d2729b8e1bee3","tid":216733,"uid":87396,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-25T11:45:10.000Z","msg":"咁點解飲半支威士忌就上晒腦?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c7e78b01e8b46744809f79e955e726fc0948265","tid":216733,"uid":43621,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-25T11:50:25.000Z","msg":"500*3*0.04 &lt; 750*0.12<br />\n答到你未"},{"pid":"6bb4c718886794772fe518bbf2378f122cb9ea48","tid":216733,"uid":87396,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-25T12:07:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>500*3*0.04 &lt; 750*0.12<br />\n答到你未</blockquote><br />\n掂喎c父<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e13fe5e1fd200a06518937693bb589f180a81abb","tid":216733,"uid":15691,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-25T12:20:44.000Z","msg":"Ching冇讀過chem?"},{"pid":"41b50ed4fcf390d28cb24bc8ead82212ebc5eb02","tid":216733,"uid":87396,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-25T16:21:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Ching冇讀過chem?</blockquote><br />\n係也